translate portuguese izzytwigtalk_03a3489c:

    # "I turn and walk away. After I take a few steps I can hear them all laughing. It's humiliating."
    "Viro-me e afasto-me. Depois de dar alguns passos, ouço-os a todos a rir. É humilhante."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:60
translate portuguese izzytwigtalk_6aa25614:

    # "Maybe I'll try again some other time, but for now I just want to get out of here."
    "Talvez tente outra vez noutra altura, mas por agora só quero sair daqui."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy1.rpy:70
